{"tid":778810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裸男在家裡自摸雞雞　慘遭警察開槍射擊","createTime":"2018-08-14T03:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T05:33:04.000Z","uid":13468,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c0e3304933a093cca88357a4ae71298ca2380b","tid":778810,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:17:52.000Z","msg":"裸男在家裡自摸雞雞　慘遭警察開槍射擊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180813/1410321/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180813%2F1410321%2F&d=8wRfes4BNiqzHQc1cLrkthv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=be538ecc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180813%2F1410321%2F&h=fec876c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180813/1410321/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國華盛頓州貝靈厄姆一處學生宿舍附近，日前有一名男子在窗邊裸體自摸下體，結果被鄰居舉報他公然自慰，警方抵達後以胡椒球子彈連環射擊，之後將他強制送醫，結果發現原來該名男子是精神有問題，撫摸下體並不是在自慰。<br />\n<br />\n據《鏡報》報導，警方在上周六下午獲報後抵達現場察看，發現男子全身赤裸，由於口頭勸說裸男離開公寓無用，警察便用漆彈槍發射胡椒球子彈，裸男被連環命中數發後縮回屋內，之後被送醫進行檢查。對面住戶在目擊過程時哈哈大笑，並拍下影片分享到推特，表示裸男一直在窗邊自慰。<br />\n<br />\n不過警方事後駁斥表示，這名男子因為瘀傷被送醫，進行精神檢查時發現他有些精神方面的問題，他赤身裸體在公寓裡雖然一度握住自己的生殖器，但並不是在自慰。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180813/640_bb39c1c5a0d8e0d65af8b241f42da3de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180813%2F640_bb39c1c5a0d8e0d65af8b241f42da3de.jpg&h=67641f1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71aab5dfa9082f56c7e914ee9bac4ccb29150827","tid":778810,"uid":32577,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:24:02.000Z","msg":"射出的不是自己的子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f06899f54a28616d609b5a738b9c6d94e31c7d9","tid":778810,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:25:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被